descp2: Iterable of weights for each of the scales. The number of scales used is the length of the list. Index 0 is the unscaled resolution's weight and each increasing scale corresponds to the image being downsampled by 2.  Defaults to (0.0448, 0.2856, 0.3001, 0.2363, 0.1333), which are the values obtained in the original paper.
